val.html:
async function parseStr(dataSet) {
  const dataArr = new XMLParser().parseFromString(dataSet).children;
  resultCount = dataArr.length; //    . (dataArr length  5  )
  setState((preState) => {
    return {
      ...preState,
      results: dataArr.slice(resultNumber, resultCount - 1),
    };
  });
  setLoaded(false);
}
